1
00:00:10,720 --> 00:00:11,400
Honey.

2
00:00:14,680 --> 00:00:16,520
Honey, are you okay?

3
00:00:16,920 --> 00:00:17,520
I'm fine.

4
00:00:17,840 --> 00:00:18,570
Don't worry.

5
00:00:30,360 --> 00:00:32,840
Honey, my eye keeps twitching.

6
00:00:33,600 --> 00:00:34,730
Left means fortune.

7
00:00:35,040 --> 00:00:35,760
Right means...

8
00:00:35,760 --> 00:00:36,680
Happiness.

9
00:00:37,840 --> 00:00:38,800
Stop worrying.

10
00:00:41,120 --> 00:00:41,920
Don't worry.

11
00:00:43,120 --> 00:00:43,920
I'm here.

12
00:01:15,440 --> 00:01:16,240
Huahua.

13
00:01:16,840 --> 00:01:17,640
Kaikai.

14
00:01:18,200 --> 00:01:20,039
Be good, babies.

15
00:01:21,520 --> 00:01:22,440
How did you know?

16
00:01:22,440 --> 00:01:23,170
I don't know.

17
00:01:25,240 --> 00:01:26,570
There's really no time.

18
00:01:30,320 --> 00:01:30,960
Sir.

19
00:01:32,479 --> 00:01:32,960
Sir.

20
00:01:34,759 --> 00:01:35,120
I...

21
00:01:35,360 --> 00:01:35,720
I...

22
00:01:35,920 --> 00:01:36,759
I'm really not a thief, Sir.

23
00:01:36,759 --> 00:01:38,360
This brat got away last time.

24
00:01:38,560 --> 00:01:39,600
Don't worry this time.

25
00:01:39,600 --> 00:01:41,160
We'll investigate thoroughly,

26
00:01:41,160 --> 00:01:42,240
and give you a satisfactory answer.

27
00:01:42,240 --> 00:01:42,840
Thank you.

28
00:01:43,240 --> 00:01:44,440
Thank you for coming.

29
00:01:56,000 --> 00:01:56,800
Wait. Wait.

30
00:02:05,520 --> 00:02:07,720
I'm begging you, brother. Let me take this call, okay?

31
00:02:07,720 --> 00:02:09,180
Sir, let me take this call.

32
00:02:13,480 --> 00:02:14,000
Shili,

33
00:02:14,520 --> 00:02:16,050
they've already left here.

34
00:02:16,440 --> 00:02:17,120
It's no good on my end.

35
00:02:17,120 --> 00:02:17,800
How about you?

36
00:02:17,800 --> 00:02:19,040
I found the truck driver,

37
00:02:19,040 --> 00:02:20,400
but he said I was crazy.

38
00:02:20,840 --> 00:02:22,320
What should we do now?

39
00:02:31,440 --> 00:02:32,240
Sun Wen.

40
00:02:33,840 --> 00:02:35,120
You have to help me.

41
00:02:41,360 --> 00:02:44,200
Xixi, the unicorn is coming to kiss you.

42
00:02:45,160 --> 00:02:46,560
It kissed you, didn't it?

43
00:02:47,840 --> 00:02:50,280
It tickles! It tickles!

44
00:02:51,480 --> 00:02:52,610
What's wrong, Xixi?

45
00:02:53,440 --> 00:02:54,160
Honey.

46
00:02:54,920 --> 00:02:56,079
Xixi takes after you.

47
00:02:56,079 --> 00:02:57,640
Quiet and well-behaved.

48
00:02:59,720 --> 00:03:02,840
If she takes after me, shouldn't she be pretty and cute?

49
00:03:04,280 --> 00:03:07,440
Right. Like you. The prettiest.

50
00:03:16,480 --> 00:03:17,840
I'm really not a bad person.

51
00:03:17,840 --> 00:03:20,370
I just want to save your husband and daughter.

52
00:03:24,880 --> 00:03:26,320
Honey? Honey?

53
00:03:28,600 --> 00:03:29,400
What's wrong?

54
00:03:32,200 --> 00:03:32,920
Honey,

55
00:03:33,440 --> 00:03:35,900
do you remember I cut my finger this morning?

56
00:03:37,240 --> 00:03:38,300
Does it still hurt?

57
00:03:41,400 --> 00:03:43,040
I just have a bad feeling.

58
00:03:43,440 --> 00:03:45,520
A man kept coming to me the last two days,

59
00:03:45,520 --> 00:03:47,200
saying that on our camping trip today,

60
00:03:47,200 --> 00:03:48,200
we'd be in danger.

61
00:03:50,840 --> 00:03:52,240
Honey, what's wrong?

62
00:03:52,520 --> 00:03:53,320
Nothing.

63
00:03:54,440 --> 00:03:58,120
There was a st... stone on the road just now.

64
00:04:02,680 --> 00:04:03,480
You...

65
00:04:04,960 --> 00:04:07,020
Don't listen to that man's nonsense.

66
00:04:07,240 --> 00:04:09,360
There are so many traffickers out there now.

67
00:04:09,360 --> 00:04:11,420
He must have seen how cute our Xixi is,

68
00:04:11,480 --> 00:04:12,360
and saw you were

69
00:04:12,360 --> 00:04:13,820
home alone with the child.

70
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:15,460
Don't get tricked by them.

71
00:04:23,040 --> 00:04:25,360
Honey, do you want to open the window for some air?

72
00:04:25,360 --> 00:04:26,160
Water.

73
00:04:27,160 --> 00:04:28,120
Me too.

74
00:04:44,440 --> 00:04:46,240
On the Guanhu Avenue you're taking today,

75
00:04:46,240 --> 00:04:47,280
there will be a car accident.

76
00:04:47,280 --> 00:04:49,540
Your husband and daughter will both die.

77
00:04:51,040 --> 00:04:54,440
Honey, will we be taking Guanhu Avenue today?

78
00:04:57,280 --> 00:04:58,560
Yes. Why?

79
00:05:00,040 --> 00:05:01,760
How about at the

80
00:05:01,760 --> 00:05:03,520
fork ahead, we take the side road?

81
00:05:03,520 --> 00:05:05,600
The air on the forest path is fresher.

82
00:05:07,880 --> 00:05:09,960
No, the small road is hard to drive on.

83
00:05:09,960 --> 00:05:11,840
It'll be dark by the time we get to the campsite.

84
00:05:11,840 --> 00:05:13,840
We still have to take Guanhu Avenue.

85
00:05:32,800 --> 00:05:34,600
It's okay.

86
00:06:16,640 --> 00:06:17,970
Do you know how to drive?

87
00:06:28,920 --> 00:06:30,840
Isn't that Jiaojiao's car?

88
00:06:30,840 --> 00:06:31,440
Jiaojiao?

89
00:06:31,880 --> 00:06:33,760
She is my girlfriend.

90
00:06:33,880 --> 00:06:36,320
I was chasing her, but I followed the wrong car.

91
00:06:36,320 --> 00:06:37,159
Sorry.

92
00:06:37,440 --> 00:06:38,720
Sorry about that, boss.

93
00:06:38,720 --> 00:06:39,720
I'm really sorry.

94
00:06:41,480 --> 00:06:42,120
Honey.

95
00:06:42,520 --> 00:06:44,400
Since we're fine, let's just go.

96
00:06:44,720 --> 00:06:45,780
Are you okay, Xixi?

97
00:06:46,000 --> 00:06:46,640
I'm fine.

98
00:06:47,920 --> 00:06:48,720
Sorry.

99
00:06:52,800 --> 00:06:54,000
Be careful next time.

100
00:06:54,440 --> 00:06:55,240
Take care.

101
00:07:32,159 --> 00:07:32,960
Mom.

102
00:07:36,040 --> 00:07:36,840
Xixi.

103
00:07:38,280 --> 00:07:39,960
My Xixi is back.

104
00:07:40,640 --> 00:07:41,520
Xixi.

105
00:07:43,360 --> 00:07:44,159
Xixi.

106
00:07:44,720 --> 00:07:45,560
Xixi.

107
00:07:52,720 --> 00:07:53,440
Is anyone there?

108
00:07:53,440 --> 00:07:55,000
Someone fell in the water! Save my wife!
